OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781657291
OL,3,CBrooklyn Beckham appears to take swipe
OL,4,Cas family feud in new advert
OL,6,FIn the advert he says: "You're
OL,7,Fprobably wondering why I'm watching
OL,8,Fthe Fifa World Cup 2026 from home"
OL,10,FHe then smiles and says: "It's a long
OL,11,Fstory."
OL,13,FThe son of the famous England
OL,14,Ffootballer can then be seen throwing
OL,15,Ftickets to a match down on a table.
OL,17,FThe Beckhams arrived in Los Angeles,
OL,18,Fwhere Brooklyn lives with his wife,
OL,19,Fearlier this week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
