OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781657291
OL,3,CBrooklyn Beckham appears to take swipe
OL,4,Cas family feud in new advert
OL,6,FCruz, Romeo and Harper were alongside
OL,7,Ftheir parents at the unveiling of
OL,8,FDavid's star on the famous Hollywood
OL,9,FWalk of Fame ahead of the World Cup.
OL,11,FDavid joined Tom Cruise and other
OL,12,Fcelebrities at the Los Angeles Stadium
OL,13,Ffor the United States' opening game
OL,14,Fwith Paraguay on Saturday. He is
OL,15,Fexpected to attend other World Cup
OL,16,Fmatches.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
