OL,3,CBrooklyn Beckham appears to take swipe
OL,4,Cas family feud in new advert
OL,6,FIn January, following months of
OL,7,Frumours, Brooklyn launched a lengthy
OL,8,Fattack on both his parents in an
OL,9,FInstagram post, accusing them of
OL,10,Fcontrolling behaviour, putting "brand
OL,11,FBeckham" before all else, and trying
OL,12,Fto "endlessly ruin" his relationship
OL,13,Fwith wife Nicola Peltz Beckham.
OL,15,FHe alleged Victoria pulled out of
OL,16,Fmaking her daughter-in-law's wedding
OL,17,Fdress at the last minute, forcing
OL,18,FPeltz to find something else to wear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
