PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781657291
OL,3,CBrooklyn Beckham appears to take swipe
OL,4,Cas family feud in new advert
OL,6,FBrooklyn also accused his mother of
OL,7,Fdancing "very inappropriately" with
OL,8,Fhim at his wedding, adding that he had
OL,9,F"never felt more uncomfortable or
OL,10,Fhumiliated in my entire life".
OL,12,FThe aspiring chef and amateur
OL,13,Fphotographer has not made a public
OL,14,Fappearance with his parents nor
OL,15,Facknowledged them on social media
OL,16,Fsince his statement, in which he also
OL,17,Fclaimed his parents control narratives
OL,18,Fin the press about their family and
OL,19,Fput "Brand Beckham" first.
