OL,3,CBrooklyn Beckham appears to take swipe
OL,4,Cas family feud in new advert
OL,6,FDJ Fat Tony revealed this week that he
OL,7,Fpublicly addressed the Beckham family
OL,8,Fdrama as he was asked to do so by
OL,9,FBrooklyn and his wife.
OL,11,FThe celebrity DJ, real name Tony
OL,12,FMarnoch, performed at Nicola and
OL,13,FBrooklyn's wedding in 2022 and
OL,14,Fappeared on ITV's This Morning earlier
OL,15,Fthis year to discuss the ongoing feud,
OL,16,Fbut admitted he had done so at the
OL,17,Frequest of the Peltz-Beckhams.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
