OL,3,CBrooklyn Beckham appears to take swipe
OL,4,Cas family feud in new advert
OL,6,FIn an interview with The Telegraph, he
OL,7,Fsaid: "I was (asked to speak).
OL,8,FThere's... a WhatsApp group,"
OL,9,Freferring to a group chat between
OL,10,Fhimself and Brooklyn and Nicola Peltz
OL,11,FBeckham.
OL,13,FThe musician, 60, continued: "I just
OL,14,Fkind of thought, you know what, I'm
OL,15,Fnot going to throw anyone under a bus,
OL,16,FI just spoke from the heart.
OL,18,F"I wasn't there to slag off Victoria
OL,19,Fand David. I wasn't spilling the beans.
OL,26,@pD@]O]
