OL,3,CBrooklyn Beckham appears to take swipe
OL,4,Cas family feud in new advert
OL,6,FGuests were said to have believed it
OL,7,Fwas for Nicola's first dance with
OL,8,FBrooklyn, but instead Lady Beckham was
OL,9,Fcalled to the stage and asked to dance
OL,10,Fwith her son, prompting Nicola to
OL,11,Fleave the room in tears.
OL,13,FVictoria addressed the feud for the
OL,14,Ffirst time in a recent interview with
OL,15,FThe Wall Street Journal, and said she
OL,16,Fand David "love our children so much"
OL,17,Fand have "always tried to be the best
OL,18,Fparents2.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
